Description: RARE Sunburst Model Fender Cabronita TELE Thinline Very Good to Excellent Comes w/ PRS gig bag Very cool sounding and playing guitar here. Good guitar for multiple music styles, Rock, Country, Jazz, hard rock, etc. Please read the specs below, thanks! An Extra-spicy Thinline Tele!Fender's Cabronita Telecaster Thinline electric guitar combines classic Tele style with a slightly rude attitude. It's got all the bark, bite, and howl you'd expect from a Thinline Tele, courtesy of its resonant chambered alder body and spanky maple neck. But, you can easily take the Cabronita Telecaster Thinline over the edge with its duo of Fideli'Tron humbucking pickups. All you need is a little tube-amp mojo and the Cabronita Telecaster Thinline's single master volume control, and you're ready to take your tone from sweet and chimey to over-the-top snarl and bite.
